        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.fixed-top.navbar-solid
            .container
                a.navbar-brand(href='index.html#page-top')
                    img(src='assets/img/navbar-logo.svg', alt='...')
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.fas.fa-bars.ms-1
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.text-uppercase.ms-auto.py-4.py-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='our-story.html') Our Story
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='location.html') Location
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='timeline.html') Timeline
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='q+a.html').active Q + A
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='rsvp.html') RSVP

        // Timeline
        section#qa.page-section.extra-margin.container
            .row.text-center 
                h2 Q+A
            .row
                .col
                .col-10.col-md-6
                    .text-center
                        p.lead I'm hungry! What will you be serving during the cruise?
                    .text-left
                        p.text-left We will be serving a light meal of small plates inspired by our Chicago favorites followed by cake. Wine, beer, cider, soft drinks, coffee, tea, and cocktails will be provided to toast our future together.
                    
                    .text-center
                        p.lead A wedding on a boat? What should I wear?
                    .text-left
                        p We kindly suggest that you dress for a "cruise to cocktail" atmosphere. We want our guests to feel elegant but comfortable, keeping in mind we will be outdoors in early summer.

                    .text-center
                        p.lead I'm arriving from out-of-town. Where should I stay?
                    .text-left
                        p We do not have specific hotel reservations. There are numerous excellent options both near the river as well as throughout the city, and we would be happy to make suggestions if needed. Feel free to #[a(href="mailto://kestella1@gmail.com") contact us directly] if you need assistance choosing a location.
                .col
                
